summary:
Having worked at various institutions and international schools in the Netherlands and abroad, I am an international educator with 10+ years of experience. Furthermore, I have gained considerable experience in leading an expat life with diplomatic status.
Being truly international-minded, I enjoy working with people of different cultural and language backgrounds, and I am always eager to pursue new opportunities.
